Configure your identity:
git config --global user.name "Your Name"
git config --global user.email "you@example.com"

Commit your changes: git commit -m "Java and Selenium codes"
clone the project from remote(git): git clone
check status of code: git status
add files: git add <file name>
add all files: git add .
pull latest changes from main branch: git pull origin main
push you code to main branch: git push origin <branch name>
then raise a PR in github
switch to branch: git checkout branchname
to fetch all branch list: git fetch --all